metadata.name: E.S.C. Ejection Pod
metadata.description: Awarded to those that held a JRNY Club and/or a Villagers of XOLO NFT at the beginning of April 2022. After experiencing troubles entering Planet XOLO's atmosphere, the crew of the E.S.C. JRNY are forced to make an emergency ejection from the destabilizing ship. These ejection pods are proof that you are one of the original JRNYers that survived the crash landing on XOLO.
